- Migraph is actively supporting companie's range of products for the 
  Amiga. Migraph makes two flatbed scanners for the Amiga that operate via
  the  SCSI port. Migraph MS1200 flatbed scanner is capable of 1200 dpi
  with software interpolation; the hardware is capable of 300x600 dpi. 
  The MS2400 flatbed scanner does single-pass color scanning. They both
  include state of the art OCR software in the package.
  Migraph even offers several hand scanners for the Amiga.

  Migraph Inc.
