- Data Compression Technologies is now offering a new version 1.20 of the
  new, powerful Amiga archiver LZX. The new version features:
 
  - Faster compression speed
  - Requires less memory
  - Can decompress Lha & Lzh files up to 35% FASTER than the registred 
    version of LHA 1.50.
  - New -9 compression mode, which compresses even better than the -3 mode.
    Going from -3 to -9 usually provides about 1.5 to 3 times the compression
    improvement of going from the default to -3
  - Asynchronous disk i/o supported for decompression, resulting in a huge
    speedup if decompressing from a hard disk or floppy disk.
  - And much more

