- Power Computing LTD is now selling 2 low cost SCSI CDROMs, x2 CD-ROM and
  x4 CD-ROM both with CD32 emulation for A600 and A1200.
  These new CDROMs for A600 and A1200 plugs directly into the PCMCIA port
  and provides a direct SCSI-I and SCSI-II interface, allowing up to six
  additional peripherals to be connected, for exmaple: Syquest drivers,
  Hard Drives, Flatbed scanners, and DAT drives. What's more the Power
  CD-ROM features a Hot-Plug and Un-Plug which allows you to connect/
  disconnect at any time the Power CDROM and any additional devices, even
  when your Amiga is switched on.
  The CDROMs come with SCSI interface, PSU, manual, audio lead, mains 
  lead and software: Audio CD, CD32 Emulation, MPEG Film decoder and
  PhotoCD software.
  
