- CONSULTRON is now shipping CrossDOS Version 6 Professional. CrossDOS has
  been enhanced to better support MS-DOS formatted floppies and hard disks.
  This new version features:

  - Faster Floppy Access
    Completely rewroten floppy device driver (mfm.device) to speed up reads
    and writes approximately two times.
  - Faster Hard Disk Writes
    Optimized CrossDOS disk caching and disk access routines to speed up
    writes to MS-DOS hard disks approximately ten times
  - Partition MS-DOS Hard Drives
    Using  the QuickPrep utility, you can create a `true' MS-DOS hard
    disk partition entirely on your Amiga. You are no longer required
    to preformat the disk on an MS-DOS computer first
  - Read and Write MS-DOS Disk Images in Files
    CrossDOS  now supports Bridgeboard MakeAB and JLink files, PC-Task
    hardfiles and AtOnce/GoldenGate diskfiles
  - Network Compatible
    This new improved CrossDOS is now compatible with most Amiga networks
  - Improved Hard Disk Configuration and Diagnostic Utilities
    Substantial  enhancements  to many CrossDOS utilities including the
    hard disk configuration and diagnostic programs
  - Full-time Technical Support
    CONSULTRON provides  full-time  technical support for theor products.
    Tech  support is available Monday through Friday between the hours
    of 10 AM and 6 PM EST.
  - Runs on any Amiga
    CrossDOS  will  run  on  any  Amiga with 512K or more of RAM using
    AmigaDOS 2.0 or higher.
  
  Priced at $60 US CrossDOS  Version  6  Professional  is available from
  most Amiga  software  retailers  or  directly  from CONSULTRON (include
  $5.00 US S&H  for  USA and Canada or $10.00 US S&H elsewhere). Visa and 
