  - Supports ILBM, LBM, RGB8/RGBN, PCX, IMG, BMP/RLE4/RLE8, GIF, TIFF, JPEG
    Targa, RGB-Raw, Postscript image formats.
  - Virtual memory on any Amiga even those without a MMU
  - Multiple language support
  - Several kinds of common image modifications are supported like
    changeing the resolution, contrast of the image or numerous color-
    effects and more.

