  - Full commodity interface. Depending on your system.
  - Supports Lha files, including extract pattern.
  - Supports Public Screens.
  - Make your own favourite lists of modules with the APML system.
  - Early load system which kills the waiting time between the modules.
  - Full ARexx interface
  - All functions in the main window is accessible via hotkeys.
