  - Backdrop Images; is useful for makeing logos and the like in the 
    Spline editor and for creation of animations that have a moving
    backdrop image.
  - FLC and ANIM brushes; you can now map to any object a FLC or ANIM.
  - SHOW PIC and ANIM; with the simple click of a mouse button you can 
    have Imagine show you any image in the formats that it reads, Anim 
    files and FLC files.
  - Field Rendering; useful for single frame recorder, of digital 
    animation system like the Personal Animation Recorder from DPS.
  - Stage Attributes; much improved.
  - Light Source and Object Viewports; view what other objects or lights
    would be seeing if they were the camera.
