- MUI, MagicUserInterface, the powerful object oriented GUI builder for
  the Amiga is now released in a version 2.3. Being writen by Stefan 
  Stuntz, the MUI v2.3 is a SASG product. From  a programmers point of
  view, using MUI saves a lot of time  and  makes life much easier. 
