- Questar Productions announces the availability of the prerelease version
  of the World Construction Set version 1.0, priced at $195 US. List price
  for the release version is $250 US. Questar Productions is currently
  updating the manual for the release version of the Questar.
  The World Construction Set is a so called terrain renderer or scenery
  generator/animator with promissing features. Highlights of WCS include
  the abililty to render the entire earth, true spline motion paths with
  a graphic editor, a complete key frame animation system with over 150
  parameters that you can animate, the ability to load and save LightWave
  motion paths, photographic rendering quality, the ability to load
  standard USGS DEM files, a style guide compliant windowing interface,
  support for high res graphics cards, and the proverbial "much more". :)
  World Construction Set (WCS) is the next generation of computer
  terrain modeling software. WCS' powerful renderer sets new standards
  in photo-realism, producing images that are often mistaken for actual
  photographs. WCS' ecosystem modeling approach combines familiar 3D
  imaging techniques with Nature's own processes to deliver scenes of
  sublime beauty and lifelike detail to your Amiga.
  World Construction Set is like nothing you have seen befor!
