- We have been informed that the OWL Software company has released yet
  another educational Amiga software, Physics Laboratory in Mechanics.
  The PLM covers kinematics, dynamics, statics, universal gravitation,
  work and energy, impulse and momentum, and rotation. 3 experiments 
  ,easy/medium/hard, are given in each subject area, with a logical 
  progression between them. One part of the program is the history and
  picture section, with a summary of the basis of the experiment and
  either its creator or the scientist who developed an important concept
  behind it.
