  will be available as soon as Motorola ships the 68060 in quantities. 
  AS&S also plans to release an 060 board running at 80Mhz as soon as the
  CPUs become available.  The Mips ratings are: A4000/40 15.447, 
  Cyberstorm 40 24.896, Cyberstorm 60 82.190. The 060 at 80Mhz is supposed
  to rate at around 130 Mips.
 
