- Custom Services is selling STU, The Amiga System Test Utiltiy. STU is a
  memory and disk diagnostic.  It tests memory and disk drives to find
  problems. STU allows you to simultaneously test up to seven disk 
  drives or partitions.  Each drive is individually controlled. You may do
  destructive or non-destructive tests.

